    "en": {
      "title": "Give international support to recover Sri Lanka from the crisis",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Indian Congress Party requested the central government and the international community to provide the necessary support to Sri Lanka to recover from the current crisis.",
        "Mrs. Sonia Gandhi, President of the Indian Congress Party, said in a statement that her party is concerned about the current political situation in Sri Lanka.",
        "The announcement shows that Sri Lankans have to face great difficulties and hardships due to the economic challenges Sri Lanka is facing, the rise in the prices of essential goods and the shortage of essential goods. The Congress Party believes that the people of Sri Lanka can overcome the current challenges and the support of the Congress Party to Sri Lanka and the people. The announcement further states that the Congress party hopes that the Government of India will continue to support the people and the government of Sri Lanka to face the current difficulties."
      ],
